title: Speedway - 1981 World Final - Wembley Stadium
description:
The 1981 World Speedway Final from Wembley Stadium, London, England. Riders on the night included:

Bruce Penhall (Cradley Heath & USA)
Kenny Carter (Halifax & England)
Michael Lee (Kings Lynn & England)
Dave Jessup (Kings Lynn & England)
Chris Morton (Belle Vue & England)
Larry Ross (Belle Vue & New Zealand)
Ales Dryml (Czechoslovakia)
Egon Muller (West Germany)
Jiri Stancl (Czechoslovakia)
Edward Jancarz (Wimbledon & Poland)
Ole Olsen (Coventry & Denmark)
Tommy Knudsen (Coventry & Denmark)
Erik Gundersen (Cradley Heath & Denmark)
Hans Nielsen (Birmingham & Denmark)
Zenon Pleach (Hackney & Poland)
Jan Andersson (Reading & Sweden)
